'''''The Secrets of Middle-earth''''' is a [[J.R.R. Tolkien|Tolkien]]-related podcast hosted by Fr. Roderick. It was formerly known as ''The Secrets of the Lord of the Rings'' but the name of the podcast was changed to ''The Secrets of Middle-earth'' on [[2 July]], [[2010]].

